    "description": "Biken Techno Corporation provides general building maintenance services in Japan. The company offers cleaning and equipment management, security services, engineering, and hygiene management; leasing management, tenant management, construction management, total maintenance, and accounting; and cleaning and sterilization services. It also offers Renovation and renewal work, repair work, and renewal construction; building management, maintenance, and building optimization; reception/call center services; quality control team services; designated manager system; and PFI/market test services. In addition, the company operates various franchise businesses, such as Mister Donut fast food shop, Tsutaya video rental shop, Pronto café and bar, and Salvatore Cuomo Italian restaurant. Further, it offers long-term care services that include visiting nursing, home help, and home care support services, as well as medical management consulting services; and manages nursing homes and nursery. Additionally, the company is involved in management of hotel; and Senior Life Business. Biken Techno Corporation was incorproated in 1963 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
